  "status": "Draft",
  "summary": "This ERC defines a standard for storing contract-level metadata onchain. It extends [ERC-7572](./eip-7572.md)'s contract-level metadata concept by providing onchain storage. Contracts MAY optionally use [ERC-8042](./eip-8042.md)'s Diamond Storage pattern for predictable storage locations, enabling cross-chain compatibility and supporting upgradable contracts.",
  "title": "Contract-Level Onchain Metadata"
